---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import "../styles/tokens.css";
---
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Matrix-Sharon · 团队技能集市</title>
    <style>
      .landing-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eceaff 0%, #e6f3ff 100%);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 56px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }
      .landing-hero h1 { font-size: 38px; margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
      .landing-hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--fg-muted); max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 28px; }
      .landing-cta { display: inline-flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }

      .feature-grid {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
      @media (max-width: 800px) { .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
      .feature-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px 22px; }
      .feature-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .feature-card h3 { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 600; }
      .feature-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }

      .quick-links {
        background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px 28px; margin-top: 32px;
      }
      .quick-links h2 { margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 18px; }
      .quick-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header active="" />
    <main class="container">
      <section class="landing-hero">
        <h1>团队的 Claude 技能，一处汇总</h1>
        <p>本地 scanner 自动发现 → leader 审核 → 一键安装到本地 → leader 推送给指定成员 → 留存率回流看板。<br/>给团队用的 Claude Code 技能集市。</p>
        <div class="landing-cta">
          <a class="btn primary big" href="/browse">→ 浏览技能</a>
          <a class="btn big" href="/me">→ 个人中心</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>浏览 & 一键安装</h3>
          <p>看团队已经审核过的高质量 skill，点一下装进 <code>~/.claude/skills/</code>，下次 Claude Code 启动就能用。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📥</div>
          <h3>本地候选自动发现</h3>
          <p>跑 <code>sharon scan</code>，你本机的 skill 自动浮到「待我决定」。一键转 submission，进 leader 审批。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>Leader 审批门</h3>
          <p>所有上架的 skill 都要 leader 批准才公开。AI 时代下，这是过滤垃圾的底层防线。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📤</div>
          <h3>精准推送给成员</h3>
          <p>Leader 可以把"必装"skill 推给指定成员，他们跑 <code>sharon receive</code> 时自动装上。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>留存率回流</h3>
          <p>谁装了、谁没装、谁卸了——leader 看到每个推送的真实留存数据，不只是"发完就完"。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
          <h3>不可变版本</h3>
          <p>每次审批通过自动生 v1 / v2 / v3，旧版本永远能装。pin 版本、回滚都顺手。</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="quick-links">
        <h2>快捷入口</h2>
        <div class="quick-row">
          <a class="btn" href="/browse">浏览技能</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/me">个人中心（候选 / 推送 / 已装 / 已发）</a>
          <a class="btn leader-only" href="/leader/queue">审批队列</a>
          <a class="btn leader-only" href="/leader/pushes">推送留存</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/settings">设置</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <style is:inline>
      .btn.leader-only { display: none; }
      body[data-role="leader"] .btn.leader-only { display: inline-flex; }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
